---
title: Warm Autumn Bacon, Butter Bean and Roasted Squash Salad with Zhoug Yoghurt and Greek Style Cheese
description: Fall in love with salads again with our Warm Autumn Bacon, Butter Bean and Roasted Squash Salad. Squash, homemade croutons, butter beans and a punchy zhoug yoghurt dressing heroes the veg and makes this perfect for autumn.
